4. role strip 状態判定仕様

初版では次の状態名に固定します。

idle

done

running

waiting

approval

stopped

failed

判定ルール案
task_router / implementer / reviewer / director

優先順:

execution_status_edit == "failed" かつ execution_role_edit が一致
→ failed

execution_role_edit が一致 かつ pipeline busy 中
→ running

detail_next_role が一致
→ waiting

inbox report にその role が存在
→ done

それ以外
→ idle

planner

優先順:

_planner_active
→ running

_pending_auto_planner_after_completion
→ waiting

_planner_report がある
→ done

stop予約で後工程スキップ状態
→ stopped

それ以外
→ idle

plan_director

優先順:

_plan_director_active
→ running

_waiting_next_task_approval
→ approval

execution_status_edit == "failed" かつ execution_role_edit == "plan_director"
→ failed

_plan_director_report がある
→ done

それ以外
→ idle

